After trying for a baby for two years, musician Loyiso Bala and his wife, Jennifer, have announced they are expecting. It will be a sibling to their daughter Kenzie, who turned four this year. Taking to Instagram, Jennifer said the couple was beyond excited. Sharing the picture on his Instagram account, Loyiso said: "God is Good. So excited that I'm going to be a daddy again". Kenzie is already one of Instagram's most-loved Mzansi children and has more than 12 000 followers.  Congratulations to the Balas!